headline: Novo Nordisk to slash GLP-1 list prices by up to 50% in U.S. to cut costs for insured patients
summary: The cuts aim to make the drugs more accessible to insured patients, particularly people with high-deductible health plans or coinsurance benefit designs.

headline: Truist Raises Cigna (CI) Price Target to $350, Sees Clearer Growth Outlook after Q4
summary: The Cigna Group (NYSE:CI) is included among the 13 Best Strong Buy Dividend Stocks to Invest in.
